{
  "stem": "7414.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I just-- They brought me-- I did not feed the baby, of course, being so sick.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they-- they fed him with an eyedropper, he was so weak.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I told my Aunt Paula to choose the names if she wants to.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she wanted very much because she wanted to name the child after her son who was killed in defense of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So his name was Lechoslaw, which is very Polish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Lechoslaw.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the other aunt wanted after her husband, Anthony.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he got Lechoslaw Anthony Koralewicz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And as you saw on his birth certificate, he's Anthony-- Lechoslaw Anthony Koralewicz from mother, not married, and-- and unknown father.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That is said.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We called him short Leszek.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That is very Polish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There were some kings which were called Leszek, Polish kings.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after two weeks in the hospital, I went home with the baby.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a very festive minute.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody was there, the whole family and everybody.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They adored the child.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at-- at this time, I had nothing to do with a child ever, but I wanted to bathe him, to feed him, and this.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was coming to my brother's.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In meantime, my brother, Henry, the younger one-- the youngest one, he was traveling.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he made a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, he was a very good businessman.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he had a way with people, you see?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One day, he came to me and he told me a story.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a man coming and going from our place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what was the connection between him and this family, but he was definitely Jewish.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was talking and looking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he wore this typical Jewish coat with a fur collar, and that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was traveling very openly all over Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
